description: Lists blueprints in an Amazon DataZone environment.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon DataZone domain.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: The results of the ListEnvironmentBlueprints action.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when an environment blueprint was created.

nested_items.name: provisioningProperties
nested_items.description: The provisioning properties of the blueprint.

nested_items.name: cloudFormation
nested_items.description: The cloud formation properties included as part of the provisioning properties of an environment blueprint.

nested_items.name: templateUrl
nested_items.description: The template URL of the cloud formation provisioning properties of the environment blueprint.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the blueprint was enabled.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When the number of blueprints in the environment is greater than the default value for the MaxResults parameter, or if you explicitly specify a value for MaxResults that is less than the number of blueprints in the environment, the response includes a pagination token named NextToken. You can specify this NextToken value in a subsequent call to ``ListEnvironmentBlueprints``to list the next set of blueprints.
